1137
00:51:32,020 --> 00:51:34,020
Now what is a photon characterized by?

1138
00:51:34,020 --> 00:51:35,020
Or a light wave.

1139
00:51:35,020 --> 00:51:37,020
Imagine a light wave coming in,

1140
