1157
00:52:15,020 --> 00:52:17,020
And the energy of one photon,

1158
00:52:18,020 --> 00:52:22,020
the energy of every single photon in this light beam,

1159
00:52:22,020 --> 00:52:25,020
with a given wavelength and a given frequency,

1160
