one of Planck's many...

1163
00:52:32,020 --> 00:52:34,020
one of Planck's constants.

1164
00:52:40,020 --> 00:52:44,020
h-bar times omega.

1165
00:52:44,020 --> 00:52:46,020
In other words,

1166
00:52:46,020 --> 00:52:48,020
