1170
00:52:53,020 --> 00:52:54,020
The larger the frequency,

1171
00:52:54,020 --> 00:52:55,020
or the shorter the wavelength,

1172
00:52:55,020 --> 00:52:59,020
the larger the energy in every photon.

1173
00:52:59,020 --> 00:53:00,020
So,

1174
00:53:00,020 --> 00:53:02,020
