1180
00:53:15,020 --> 00:53:16,020
There's no question.

1181
00:53:16,020 --> 00:53:18,020
You can make radio waves with lots of energy.

1182
00:53:18,020 --> 00:53:21,020
Lots and lots of energy.

1183
00:53:21,020 --> 00:53:24,020
