1192
00:53:44,020 --> 00:53:46,020
This is the energy of a photon.

1193
00:53:46,020 --> 00:53:49,020
The energy of a light ray,

1194
00:53:49,020 --> 00:53:51,020
let's just call it a ray,

1195
00:53:51,020 --> 00:53:53,020
or a light wave,

1196
00:53:53,020 --> 00:53:55,020
is some integer number,

1197
00:53:55,020 --> 00:53:57,020
some integer multiple

1198
00:53:57,020 --> 00:53:59,020
of h bar omega.

1199
00:53:59,020 --> 00:54:03,020
Alright, so the light rays come in indivisible units.

1200
00:54:03,020 --> 00:54:04,020
Every light ray,

1201
00:54:04,020 --> 00:54:05,020
every light wave,

1202
00:54:05,020 --> 00:54:07,020
every pulse of light

1203
00:54:07,020 --> 00:54:11,020
with a given frequency and wavelength

1204
00:54:11,020 --> 00:54:14,020
has an integer multiple of energy

1205
00:54:14,020 --> 00:54:15,020
in units of light.

1206
00:54:15,020 --> 00:54:18,020
In units of h bar omega.

1207
00:54:18,020 --> 00:54:20,020
