1294
00:58:19,020 --> 00:58:21,020
So there's something wrong with this equation.

1295
00:58:21,020 --> 00:58:23,020
Yes, there's something wrong with this equation.

1296
00:58:23,020 --> 00:58:26,020
This equation is no longer...

