00:58:31,020 --> 00:58:34,020
At least with modern terminology.

1300
00:58:34,020 --> 00:58:37,020
Energy is only equal to mass times c squared

1301
00:58:37,020 --> 00:58:39,020
for an object at rest.

1302
00:58:40,020 --> 00:58:43,020
The right way to say it

1303
00:58:43,020 --> 00:58:46,020
is the energy of an object at rest

1304
00:58:46,020 --> 00:58:50,020
