1311
00:59:03,020 --> 00:59:05,020
then we speak of its rest mass,

1312
00:59:05,020 --> 00:59:08,020
and we can speak of its rest energy,

1313
00:59:08,020 --> 00:59:10,020
the energy of that box of gas,

1314
00:59:10,020 --> 00:59:12,020
when it's standing still.

1315
00:59:12,020 --> 00:59:14,020
And Einstein's equation says that

1316
00:59:14,020 --> 00:59:16,020
